abstract: Asian stocks pushed higher early Thursday, as a strong showing on United States markets inspired investors to unwind some of the recent damage.

lead_paragraph: SINGAPORE, Thursday, Aug. 23 (Dow Jones) — Asian stocks pushed higher early Thursday, as a strong showing on United States markets inspired investors to unwind some of the recent damage.

headline.main: Asian Stocks Up in Early Trading, Buoyed by Rise on Wall Street
